  "title": "Operations Control Analyst (1 year contract) - Bank",
  "description": "<ul><li>An exciting opportunity with one of the global top private bank.</li><li>12 months contract with chances of extension.</li></ul><h2>About Our Client</h2><p>My client is one of the leading private banks globally specialising exclusively in private banking and wealth management, serving high‑net‑worth and ultra‑high‑net‑worth clients.</p><h2>Job Description</h2><ul><li>Collaborate with internal teams and relevant stakeholders to support data extraction, MIS reporting, audits, and regulatory data requests.</li><li>Ensure accurate and timely submission of regulatory reports for OTC derivative products.</li><li>Support sub‑account setup for Trade Processing and Corporate Actions teams.</li><li>Ensure all data extracts are provided strictly on a need‑to‑know basis, with appropriate approvals and control checks in place.</li><li>Participate in UAT activities as required.</li></ul><h2>The Successful Applicant</h2><ul><li>Bachelor's degree in relevant field</li><li>At least 2 years of experience within Banking industry</li></ul><h2>What's on Offer</h2><ul><li>Temporary role within a reputable organisation in the financial services industry.</li><li>Opportunity for extension.</li></ul><p>Contact</p><p>Ginny Teo (Lic No: R22104515/ EA no: 18C9065)</p><p>Quote job ref</p><p>JN-012026-6932839</p><p>Phone number</p><p>+65 6541 9926</p>",
